'cs_title','ABI Services'),(1861,157,'_cs_title','field_5760044152c8e'),(1862,157,'cs_subtitle','Unified communication and data networks'),(1863,157,'_cs_subtitle','field_5760044c52c8f'),(1864,157,'cs_excerpt','ABI (Acquired Brain Injury) Services is a not for profit business specializing in providing services to people with an acquired brain injury.'),(1865,157,'_cs_excerpt','field_5760048152c90'),(1874,155,'cs_thumbnail_image','227'),(1875,155,'_cs_thumbnail_image','field_576003e652c8d'),(1876,155,'cs_title','Kel Campbell'),(1877,155,'_cs_title','field_5760044152c8e'),(1878,155,'cs_subtitle',''),(1879,155,'_cs_subtitle','field_5760044c52c8f'),(1880,155,'cs_excerpt','During 2013, TechnologyFX began working with Kel Campbell to implement new technologies, beginning with a Hosted Server platform to house a new CRM. The current platform was ageing and with a need for reliance on local hardware becoming outdated, a new landscape was required.'),(1881,155,'_cs_excerpt','field_5760048152c90'),(1882,154,'cs_thumbnail_image','226'),(1883,154,'_cs_thumbnail_image','field_576003e652c8d'),(1884,154,'cs_title','Colquhoun\'s'),(1885,154,'_cs_title','field_5760044152c8e'),(1886,154,'cs_subtitle','IT system strategy and implementation'),(1887,154,'_cs_subtitle','field_5760044c52c8f'),(1888,154,'cs_excerpt','Colquhoun’s is a fifth generation Australian company with a long history of leadership in the packaging industry. When TechnologyFX was introduced to the business the technology in play was far from optimal and built predominantly on legacy systems.'),(1889,154,'_cs_excerpt','field_5760048152c90'),(1890,153,'cs_thumbnail_image','225'),(1891,153,'_cs_thumbnail_image','field_576003e652c8d'),(1892,153,'cs_title','Capital Chemist'),(1893,153,'_cs_title','field_5760044152c8e'),(1894,153,'cs_subtitle','Technology solutions at the group level'),(1895,153,'_cs_subtitle','field_5760044c52c8f'),(1896,153,'cs_excerpt','In 2008 TechnologyFX had an opportunity to consult with the Capital Chemist Group based\r\n\r\nin Canberra, ACT. TechnologyFX had previously worked on a transactional basis with\r\n\r\nmembers of the group but was asked to put forward a standard offering covering the\r\n\r\nbest practices in managing the technology solutions at the group level and at the\r\n\r\nindividual store level.'),(1897,153,'_cs_excerpt','field_5760048152c90'),(1898,231,'_edit_last','1'),(1899,231,'_edit_lock','1465973475:1'),(1900,157,'challenge_title',''),(1901,157,'_challenge_title','field_5760aef22f0f6'),(1902,157,'challenge_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">ABI (Acquired Brain Injury) Services is a not for profit business specializing in providing services to people with an acquired brain injury. With both an office-based and mobile workforce, technology was key to ensuring compliance, rostering and smooth, continuous service delivery.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">For the Sydney based head office and a rural secondary office, communication between the sites is key and is an area TechnologyFX have assisted with greatly. From voice to data connections, TechnologyFX have ensured minimal downtime of the unified communication and data networks.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">As hardware ages, TechnologyFX provided timely consulting services to determine the best way forward with an economic and scalable solution encompassing replacement hardware and the migration of some critical services to the cloud.</p>'),(1903,157,'_challenge_description','field_5760af602f0f7'),(1904,157,'challenge_image','1854'),(1905,157,'_challenge_image','field_5760af782f0f8'),(1906,236,'_wp_attached_file','2016/06/cs_abi_image-hero.jpg'),(1907,236,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:470;s:6:\"height\";i:620;s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"2016/06/cs_abi_image-hero.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"cs_abi_image-hero-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4: