dful of working within the budget accessible to not for profit organisations when designing required solutions. Hosted Exchange for email combined with a lower specification server platform, provided the perfect solution to take ABI forward with confidence into the next 4 years. TechnologyFX Professional Services Team delivered both solutions to completion whilst maintaining full transparency and communication. Additional technology areas from the Office 365 platform are still being utilized for collaboration and information sharing within the organization.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">The new platform is now fully maintained by TechnologyFX Managed Services with minimal support requirements and outages. ABI Services has expressed the most important part of TechnologyFX being our people that support them. They know we are always there and available to help through any technical issue, whether a simple question or a more complex problem.</p>'),(1921,157,'_solution_description','field_5760b13e44827'),(1922,157,'solution_download_link',''),(1923,157,'_solution_download_link','field_5760b15644828'),(1924,157,'solution_results_0_solution_result','Reduction in ICT spend'),(1925,157,'_solution_results_0_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(1926,157,'solution_results_1_solution_result','Empowerment of remote/mobile users'),(1927,157,'_solution_results_1_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(1928,157,'solution_results_2_solution_result','Reduction in down time'),(1929,157,'_solution_results_2_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(1930,157,'solution_results_3_solution_result','Improved staff collaboration'),(1931,157,'_solution_results_3_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(1932,157,'solution_results_4_solution_result','Enhanced client engagement'),(1933,157,'_solution_results_4_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(1934,157,'solution_results_5_solution_result','Reduction of time spent on ICT'),(1935,157,'_solution_results_5_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(1936,157,'solution_results_6_solution_result','Reduction of business risk'),(1937,157,'_solution_results_6_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(1938,157,'solution_results','7'),(1939,157,'_solution_results','field_5760b17444829'),(1940,157,'solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','TechnologyFX Managed Services'),(1941,157,'_solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(1942,157,'solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','Microsoft Office 365'),(1943,157,'_solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(1944,157,'solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','Windows Server and Active Directory'),(1945,157,'_solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(1946,157,'solution_technologies','3'),(1947,157,'_solution_technologies','field_5760b1994482b'),(1948,249,'_edit_last','1'),(1949,249,'_edit_lock','1465955268:1'),(1950,157,'cs_testimonial_by','Daniel Stafford, Acquired Brain Injury Services NSW Inc.'),(1951,157,'_cs_testimonial_by','field_5760b38c5a50a'),(1952,157,'cs_testimonial_description','I just wanted to take a moment to let you know how we as an organisation are continually impressed by the excellent support service that TechnologyFX provides.\r\n\r\nHaving changed our IT support to TechnologyFX in 2008, (we have now been with you for 8 years), I sit back and think about our relationship and realise that it has truly has been a great one. Our IT system has been unbelievably stable. We have minimal computer issues now, and this has reduced our costs enormously and made our organisation more streamlined and efficient.\r\n\r\nI think the most important part of TechnologyFX is its people that support us. They are always there and available to help us get through any technical issues we may have. From a simple question on hardware or software to assisting with solving very complex solutions.\r\n\r\nIt makes a pleasant change to deal with a company that takes pride in providing your level of IT support. \r\n\r\nThank you TechnologyFX , your support and service have been exceptional!\r\n'),(1953,157,'_cs_testimonial_description','field_5760b3b25a50b'),(1996,155,'challenge_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">During 2013, TechnologyFX began working with Kel Campbell to implement new technologies, beginning with a Hosted Server platform to house a new CRM. The current platform was ageing and with a need for reliance on local hardware becoming outdated, a new landscape was required.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">With the success of the hosted CRM, further movement of applications from local infrastructure was required for security, longevity and growth whilst providing a solid foundation for business growth. Seamless connectivity of 5 remote sites was another challenge that TechnologyFX worked closely with Kel Campbell to manage whilst also providing scope for additional sites to be added to the network.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">Migration of email was the next project that TechnologyFX managed for Kel Campbell. Remote connectivity, redundancy and security were are high priorities for email and a hosted email solution was deemed the most suitable.</p>'),(1997,155,'_challenge_description','field_5760af602f0f7'),(1998,155,'challenge_image','240'),(1999,155,'_challenge_image','field_5760af782f0f8'),(2000,155,'cs_testimonial_by','TIM CAMPBELL, MANAGING DIRECTOR'),(2001,155,'_cs_testimonial_by','field_5760b38c5a50a'),(2002,155,'cs_testimonial_description','“The customer service we receive during each project is always friendly and of a high standard. I can highly recommend their services”'),(2003,155,'_cs_testimonial_description','field_5760b3b25a50b'),(2004,155,'solution_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">TechnologyFX began from the ground up and implemented a private network which then formed the solid platform on which to build a robust infrastructure. Hosted servers were provisioned and configured using TechnologyFX expertise while continuing close liaison with both software vendors and Kel Campbell. This allowed the ISV to build their application in a secure and accessible environment and develop a positive, collaborative relationship with TechnologyFX in the process.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">The next challenge was to connect all the remote petrol stations to the head office network. TechnologyFX worked closely with Kel Campbell and Telstra to bring together this solution. We worked through issues together and achieved a strong end result. Due to the ageing hardware and software technology at Kel Campbell, a move to Office 365 for email was the next step forward. TechnologyFX managed this project for email migration with minimal downtime and disruption to business with an excellent end result.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">Since the relationship began, Kel Campbell required a partner who can deliver ongoing managed services to remove the day to day issues from the company director. TechnologyFX has delivered and continues to build managed services into the business model, enabling Kel Campbell to achieve their growth goals and successful vision.</p>'),(2005,155,'_solution_description','field_5760b13e44827'),(2006,155,'solution_download_link',''),(2007,155,'_solution_download_link','field_5760b15644828'),(2008,155,'solution_results','7'),(2009,155,'_solution_results','field_5760b17444829'),(2010,155,'solution_technologies','6'),(2011,155,'_solution_technologies','field_5760b1994482b'),(2012,155,'solution_results_0_solution_result','Improved Connectivity'),(2013,155,'_solution_results_0_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2014,155,'solution_results_1_solution_result','Enhanced Security'),(2015,155,'_solution_results_1_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2016,155,'solution_results_2_solution_result','Reduction in Capital Outlay'),(2017,155,'_solution_results_2_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2018,155,'solution_results_3_solution_result','Improved redundancy'),(2019,155,'_solution_results_3_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2020,155,'solution_results_4_solution_result','More Time for Business Operations'),(2021,155,'_solution_results_4_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2022,155,'solution_results_5_solution_result','Great Expansion Capability'),(2023,155,'_solution_results_5_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2024,155,'solution_results_6_solution_result','Reduction of Business Risk'),(2025,155,'_solution_results_6_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2026,155,'solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','TechnologyFX Managed Services'),(2027,155,'_solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2028,155,'solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','Microsoft Office 365'),(2029,155,'_solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2030,155,'solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','Telstra Managed Network'),(2031,155,'_solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2032,155,'solution_technologies_3_solution_technology','Microsoft Windows Server'),(2033,155,'_solution_technologies_3_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2034,155,'solution_technologies_4_solution_technology','TechnologyFX Professional Services'),(2035,155,'_solution_technologies_4_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2036,155,'solution_technologies_5_solution_technology','Microsoft Group Policy'),(2037,155,'_solution_technologies_5_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2038,154,'challenge_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">Colquhoun’s is a fifth generation Australian company with a long history of leadership in the packaging industry. When TechnologyFX was introduced to the business the technology in play was far from optimal and built predominantly on legacy systems.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">In addition the company, with its multiple Australian offices, was struggling to deliver standards and quickly resolve technology problems as they emerged. The company had a long tradition of maintaining local infrastructure and the policy was starting to hinder the company’s ability to trade and make agile moves.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">This was particularly pronounced with its large group of remote users and travelling staff. The challenge was how do you align new company direction in a disrupted market, without the right technology strategies in place to support such maneuvering?</p>'),(2039,154,'_challenge_description','field_5760af602f0f7'),(2040,154,'challenge_image','239'),(2041,154,'_challenge_image','field_5760af782f0f8'),(2042,154,'cs_testimonial_by','ROBERT COLQUHOUN, MANAGING DIRECTOR COLQUHOUN’S'),(2043,154,'_cs_testimonial_by','field_5760b38c5a50a'),(2044,154,'cs_testimonial_description','“Since we engaged TechnologyFX to take care of our IT Solutions we have reaped a large benefit in terms of service outages, repair costs, support and project management. We now run an IT System that is the envy of others!”'),(2045,154,'_cs_testimonial_description','field_5760b3b25a50b'),(2046,154,'solution_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">TechnologyFX worked on an ICT Strategy very rapidly with the company’s Managing Director and leadership team. The strategy needed to handle the challenge of consolidating company costs whilst providing the company more output and agile solutions. A detailed analysis was done of a cloud strategy, on premise strategy and a hybrid approach. It wasn’t long before the benefits of cloud were apparent particularly after the company suffered a number of concerning outages due to old infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">Managed services were rolled out in tandem with a number of shifts to the cloud across the business key applications and the adoption of Office 365. With a consolidated approach that meant the sites were now aligned to a hosted solution, the company was soon able to start to reduce time and risk tied up around technology. A key solution was to enable remote and mobile users to be active at client sites and during their travels.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">In addition with better usage of the companies systems and a dedicated partner in TechnologyFX , users gained morale and were quickly able to resolve issues and learn to harness systems quicker. Even small things like reduction on power bills helped make an enormous different to the overall technology costs.</p>'),(2047,154,'_solution_description','field_5760b13e44827'),(2048,154,'solution_download_link',''),(2049,154,'_solution_download_link','field_5760b15644828'),(2050,154,'solution_results_0_solution_result','Reduction in ICT Spend'),(2051,154,'_solution_results_0_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2052,154,'solution_results_1_solution_result','Empowerment of Remote/Mobile Users'),(2053,154,'_solution_results_1_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2054,154,'solution_results_2_solution_result','Reduction in Down Time'),(2055,154,'_solution_results_2_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2056,154,'solution_results_3_solution_result','Improved Staff collaboration'),(2057,154,'_solution_results_3_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2058,154,'solution_results_4_solution_result','Enhanced Client Engagement'),(2059,154,'_solution_results_4_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2060,154,'solution_results_5_solution_result','Reduction of Time Spent on ICT'),(2061,154,'_solution_results_5_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2062,154,'solution_results_6_solution_result','Reduction of Business Risk'),(2063,154,'_solution_results_6_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2064,154,'solution_results','7'),(2065,154,'_solution_results','field_5760b17444829'),(2066,154,'solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','TechnologyFX Managed Services'),(2067,154,'_solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2068,154,'solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','Microsoft Office 365'),(2069,154,'_solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2070,154,'solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','Telstra Business Network'),(2071,154,'_solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2072,154,'solution_technologies_3_solution_technology','Telstra IP Telephony (TIPT)'),(2073,154,'_solution_technologies_3_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2074,154,'solution_technologies_4_solution_technology','Windows Server and Active Directory'),(2075,154,'_solution_technologies_4_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2076,154,'solution_technologies_5_solution_technology','Pronto ERP and CRM'),(2077,154,'_solution_technologies_5_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2078,154,'solution_technologies','6'),(2079,154,'_solution_technologies','field_5760b1994482b'),(2080,153,'challenge_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">In 2008 TechnologyFX had an opportunity to consult with the Capital Chemist Group based in Canberra, ACT. TechnologyFX had previously worked on a transactional basis with members of the group but was asked to put forward a standard offering covering the best practices in managing the technology solutions at the group level and at the individual store level.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">As a growing Pharmacy Chain operating in the community sector, Capital began to recognize the need for solid and consistent IT Services and a partner with the capability to put forward strong IT solutions. The group also decided that it was time to consolidate systems and embrace big data, this covered Point of Sale and Dispense systems.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">In recent times the group also wanted to execute a good solution around adopting the cloud and bring better collaboration to the many members to the group.</p>'),(2081,153,'_challenge_description','field_5760af602f0f7'),(2082,153,'challenge_image','238'),(2083,153,'_challenge_image','field_5760af782f0f8'),(2084,153,'cs_testimonial_by','PETER DOWNING, GROUP BUSINESS MANAGER, CAPITAL CHEMIST'),(2085,153,'_cs_testimonial_by','field_5760b38c5a50a'),(2086,153,'cs_testimonial_description','“The TechnologyFX team are reliable, professional and act promptly to assist with any issues. In our view TechnologyFX is the leading provider of IT Installation, support and maintenance to the community pharmacy sector”'),(2087,153,'_cs_testimonial_description','field_5760b3b25a50b'),(2088,153,'solution_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">TechnologyFX engaged at the group level and at the store level to build understanding of the client’s business model and their unique requirements. It was clear from the outset that the customer required a standardized solution so that the business could build a template for all sites with a robust base. HP Point of Sale was architected including a strong server solution so that each site would have redundancy and commercially graded equipment to handle the rigors of a busy retail and pharmacy environment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">A big part of handling the company’s requirement was building a customized managed services solution so that site issues would be picked up quickly and managed in a proactive manner. This resolved issues quickly and improved downtime rates across the group.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">At the group level work was done to assist the consolidation and rollout of a single point of sale solution that would align all sites to a single data point allowing the group to gain large benefits from Big Data and an improved logistics solution.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">To leverage the cloud, TechnologyFX rolled out a Microsoft 365 solution and built in virtualized server technology to managed central applications and data storage. Redundancy and security management was handled by TechnologyFX managed solution preventing security breaches and data loss.</p>'),(2089,153,'_solution_description','field_5760b13e44827'),(2090,153,'solution_download_link',''),(2091,153,'_solution_download_link','field_5760b15644828'),(2092,153,'solution_results_0_solution_result','Significant reduction in outage times'),(2093,153,'_solution_results_0_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2094,153,'solution_results_1_solution_result','Speed of operating practices increased'),(2095,153,'_solution_results_1_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2096,153,'solution_results_2_solution_result','Reduced unplanned ICT spending'),(2097,153,'_solution_results_2_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2098,153,'solution_results_3_solution_result','Improved store margins'),(2099,153,'_solution_results_3_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2100,153,'solution_results_4_solution_result','Improved speed of ordering and supply'),(2101,153,'_solution_results_4_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2102,153,'solution_results_5_solution_result','Higher levels of security'),(2103,153,'_solution_results_5_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2104,153,'solution_results_6_solution_result','Increased group collaboration'),(2105,153,'_solution_results_6_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2106,153,'solution_results','7'),(2107,153,'_solution_results','field_5760b17444829'),(2108,153,'solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','TechnologyFX Managed Services'),(2109,153,'_solution_technologies_0_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2110,153,'solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','Aerohive Wireless Solution'),(2111,153,'_solution_technologies_1_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2112,153,'solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','Telstra Business Network'),(2113,153,'_solution_technologies_2_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2114,153,'solution_technologies_3_solution_technology','Microsoft Office 365'),(2115,153,'_solution_technologies_3_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2116,153,'solution_technologies_4_solution_technology','Posworks Point of Sale'),(2117,153,'_solution_technologies_4_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2118,153,'solution_technologies_5_solution_technology','HP Retail POS'),(2119,153,'_solution_technologies_5_solution_technology','field_5760b1ae4482c'),(2120,153,'solution_technologies','6'),(2121,153,'_solution_technologies','field_5760b1994482b'),(2122,143,'challenge_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">In 2007 Blooms the Chemist approached TechnologyFX for support on a sizeable technical challenge. A growing pharmacy chain, Blooms the Chemist was looking to build an ICT strategy that would allow for future growth and the ability to manage technology from a central place.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">Amongst the challenges was the sizeable concern about the lack of standards in the group and the number of different applications. Due to the nature of the organically growing business, technology had taken a life of its own leaving the Support Office with frustration over the inability to measure business metrics accurately and on time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">Data was present but in different shapes, sizes and versions leaving a combined business intelligence approach almost impossible. This meant understanding trends and measuring results was limited. In addition the infrastructure was prone to fail resulting in stores losing valuable trading time and frustrating both operators and clientele.</p>'),(2123,143,'_challenge_description','field_5760af602f0f7'),(2124,143,'challenge_image','237'),(2125,143,'_challenge_image','field_5760af782f0f8'),(2126,143,'cs_testimonial_by','ELISE TURNER, COMMUNICATIONS & DIGITAL MANAGER'),(2127,143,'_cs_testimonial_by','field_5760b38c5a50a'),(2128,143,'cs_testimonial_description','“TechnologyFX Solutions has been our Key IT Partner since 2007. I have found TechnologyFX to be a very responsive and committed partner and would have no hesitation in recommended them as an IT Partner.”'),(2129,143,'_cs_testimonial_description','field_5760b3b25a50b'),(2130,143,'solution_description','<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">TechnologyFX immediately looked at collating the problems and understanding the priorities in which the challenges needed to be addressed. Shortly after building the first ICT strategy, TechnologyFX started with unifying the network and giving the company a single service desk to handle issues and manage infrastructure. This unification process was handled in under 100 days and provided the Support Office with a single place to go to for information and business intelligence on the state of the network.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">In addition a proactive system was built to detect problems at each site before they became major outages. Through a single dashboard all jobs and issues were handled and systems monitored. This provided the business with the opportunity to start to isolate problematic issues and fix them quickly and economically. Shortly after the business was able to rollout store standards and efficiently upgrade each site to ensure optimal operating conditions. Once the network was running efficiently and stores were on an upgrade path a number of projects started to develop especially focusing on consolidation of applications and the implementation of cloud solutions such as Office 365.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l-p--left-align\">Not long after the business had successfully consolidated to a single Point of Sale solution and dispensing systems. This allowed the group to leverage data quickly bringing huge efficiencies in logistics, purchasing and focused marketing.</p>'),(2131,143,'_solution_description','field_5760b13e44827'),(2132,143,'solution_download_link',''),(2133,143,'_solution_download_link','field_5760b15644828'),(2134,143,'solution_results_0_solution_result','Significant reduction in outage times'),(2135,143,'_solution_results_0_solution_result','field_5760b18a4482a'),(2136,143,'solution_results_1_solution_result','Speed of operating practices increased'),(2